ing (very light desires, disli=\r\nkes etc) can protect one as one&#39;s Kundalini rises to meet True Self. Heavy =\r\nconditioning and impurities in one&#39;s nadis will distract rising Kundalini (=\r\nself-awareness) and stop Her from meeting True Self.\n=C2=A0\nThe real key is=\r\n how light your conditioning is.\n=C2=A0\nBest regards,\nNarasimha\n--------\nAs=\r\ntrology & Spirituality Resources: http://www.VedicAstrologer.org\n--------\n\n=\r\n=C2=A0\n\n\n&gt;________________________________\n&gt; From: Leela Sastry &lt;leela.sast=\r\nry@...&gt;\n&gt;To: &quot;vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com&quot; &lt;vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups=\r\n.com&gt; \n&gt;Sent: Thursday, February 28, 2013 6:05 AM\n&gt;Subject: Re: [vedic-wisd=\r\nom] Kundalini syndrome\n&gt; \n&gt;\n&gt;=C2=A0 \n&gt;=C2=A0YES=C2=A0 SIR=C2=A0 , perfectly=\r\n correct=C2=A0=C2=A0 ,=C2=A0but intense bhakthi and saranagathi=C2=A0 makes=\r\n the ishtadevatha to stand by the sadhaka and remove most of the hurdles .=\r\n=C2=A0=C2=A0All the so called dhyanamargas with out any personal deity and =\r\nmanthra allow the other entities to enter in to the inner planes who play h=\r\navoc with the=C2=A0 psyche .=C2=A0 Once we are under the protection of=C2=\r\n=A0 a mahadevatha ,all the other=C2=A0 disturbances will definitely=C2=A0 b=\r\ne wiped off . But=C2=A0 it can be attained by the righteous behaviour along=\r\n with manthranushtana . You have explained very nicely .=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=\r\n=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0 regards ls .=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0\n&gt;\n&gt;From: rajarshi n=\r\nandy &lt;rajarshi14@...&gt;\n&gt;&gt;To: &quot;vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com&quot; &lt;vedic-w=\r\nisdom@yahoogroups.com&gt; \n&gt;&gt;Sent: Thursday, February 28, 2013 4:20 PM\n&gt;&gt;Subje=\r\nct: Re: [vedic-wisdom] Kundalini syndrome\n&gt;&gt;\n&gt;&gt;=C2=A0 \n&gt;&gt;In Tantra, to focu=\r\ns on Kundalini, one needs a few things going. 1 - Bhuta Suddhi. Constant ef=\r\nforts of purification of the various elements that compose the human mind